dsDescriptionValue.value: The folder has the seventeen network datasets we used for a network regression task. The folder contains the files used for a 5-cross validation experiment replicated by 5 trials. The datasets are organized in 4 categories of files: namefile_arffTest_N (the testing file for the trial N-th), namefile_arffTrain_M (the training file for the trial M-th), namefile_arffTrain_P_arffSampleQ (the sample for Q-th trial at P-th fold). Also, a file of the distances of the edges is associated to each dataset.
